title: HOUR 1- Chris Mannix Sep 23, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 1- Chris Mannix Sep 23, 2020
description:
Chris Mannix tells Dan that the Denver Nuggets should be feeling really confident because they could be leading the series 2 games to 1. Mannix says that the Lakers have to dominate the boards or they might as well play Anthony Davis at the 5 position.
